                        <desc><desc>Careful but not very regular; by a mediocre scribe.
                          Broad bulky script. Downstrokes are right-sloping, tops are horizontal.
                          Rectangular letter shapes. The top of ጥ is flat (e.g. <locus target="#5r"/>, <locus target="#18r"/>
                          <locus target="#31v"/>); the left leg of ለ is leant upon the right leg.
                           Gaps between elements of many letters.</desc></desc>

